<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<% include ../partials/head %>
		<title>MikalBot</title>
		<meta property="og:title" content="MikalBot">
		<meta name="description" content="A chat bot that spices up your Facebook group chats!">
		<meta property="og:description" content="A chat bot that spices up your Facebook group chats!">
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<% include ../partials/navbar %>
		</header>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="jumbotron">
				<h1>Welcome to MikalBot</h1>
			</div>
			
			<div class="page-header">
				<h3>So, what is MikalBot?</h3>
			</div>
			<p><b>MikalBot</b> is a Facebook chat bot that does a lot of cool things! Check <a href="/about#help">this page</a> for a list of commands. MikalBot is currently part of <b><%= N %></b> chat<% if (N > 1) { %>s<% } %>.</p>
			
			<div class="page-header">
				<h3>Join my chat?</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Add me to any of your group chats! When Facebook asks you to enter a friend's name, enter this email instead: <code>mikal.zaeng@gmail.com</code>. That's all you need to get MikalBot up and running!</p>
			<p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Mikal-Zaeng/100011307603181" title="Mikal Zaeng" target="_TOP"><img class="img" src="https://badge.facebook.com/badge/100011307603181.11016.1370130857.png" style="border: 0px;" alt="" /></a></p>
			
			<div class="page-header">
				<h3>Friend me?</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Sure! I'm open to friend requests. I'll probably need them to make Facebook think my account is 100% legit.</p>
			
			<div class="page-header">
				<h3>How do I check my rankings?</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Go get your <b>thread ID</b>. View your rankings at <code>/stats/&lt;thread id&gt;</code>. Or just type <b>!leaderboard</b> in your chat.</p>
			
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="page-header">
					<h3>Gimme Some Likes</h3>
				</div>
				<p><div class="fb-like" data-share="true" data-width="450" data-show-faces="true"></div></p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-6">
				<div class="page-header">
					<h3>Donate?</h3>
				</div>
				<p>Donations will go towards getting a domain and dedicated server. Account-based donations coming soon!</p>
				<form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
					<input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
					<input type="hidden" name="encrypted" value="-----BEGIN PKCS7----------END PKCS7-----
					">
					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-success">Donate!</button>
					<!-- <input type="image" src="http://placehold.it/600x100" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!"> -->
					<img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
				</form>
			</div>
			
			<div class="page-header">
				<h3>Privacy</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Your chats aren't recorded and we won't read the chats. The bot is simply tracking how often you talk.</p>
		</div>
		<footer>
			<% include ../partials/footer %>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>